HEADWORD: Bewonder
<hw>Be*won"der</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Bewondered</conjf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.]</vmorph>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>To fill with wonder.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To wonder at; to admire.</def>
